  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Provision of a senior loan of up to USD 70 million to Zorlu Dogal Elektrik  Uretimi A.S. (Zorlu Dogal) guaranteed by Zorlu Enerji Elektrik Uretimi A.S.  (Zorlu Enerji) and Zorlu Holding A.i. (Zorlu Holding). The transaction is part  of an up to USD 270 million financing package to be used for the construction  of the 70MW Kizildere III Unit 2 geothermal power plant located in West  Anatolia, Turkey.</narrative>
